Package de.joemiagroup.krawumm

Class Experiment

java.lang.Object
de.joemiagroup.krawumm.ExperimentData
de.joemiagroup.krawumm.Experiment
Record Components:
name - is the name of the experiment
material - is an array which contains the Materials needed for the experiments
description - contains a short description text for the experiment (max 500 characters)
pictures - contains pictures of the experiment
indoorOutdoor - is 1 for indoor and 2 for outdoor
age - holds the minimum age the child should be to do the experiment
duration - holds the estimated time it takes to finish the experiment
difficulty - holds a difficulty value between 1 and 5 (5 is hardest)
video - contains vidoes of the experiment
instruction - contains a instruction of the steps to do the experiment
creator - holds a reference to the RegisteredUsser who uploaded this experiment
finalRating - holds the calculated average of all ratings combined
rating - contains all ratings of this experiment
comments - contains all comments of this experiment
public class Experiment
extends ExperimentData
This class is a Subclass od ExperimentData gets attributes(+setter and getter)(same as used in Form) adds attributes finalRating ,rating and comments which only needed for a released Experiment(not for a Form)
Author:
Johannes Otto
